{"tid":1531634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者對於陀槍“示威者”應該問既問題","createTime":"2019-09-02T09:39:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T10:41:11.000Z","uid":265863,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"54800204f66fb21f5f1d17d389df4f45e271cc87","tid":1531634,"uid":265863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:39:46.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n四點狗會已經連續兩日強烈否認影到陀槍既&ldquo;示威者&ldquo; 係警犬<br />\n但係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係冇講過</span></span>點解佢地唔集中警力拘捕佢<br />\n因為佢唔止飛cocktail, 仲要陀住一把疑似真炮既物件<br />\n如果觀星筆，遮都可以話係攻擊性武器 做拉人理據<br />\n點解警犬唔即時拎出黎煲大佢？唔即刻開始調查塔鳩佢？<br />\n好明顯係身有屎 呢啲完全係司馬昭之心<br />\n所以記者朋友唔應該繼續咬住問佢係咪警犬（一定繼續三幅屁否認）<br />\n而係要問<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>&ldquo;點解你口中個所謂真示威者陀埋槍你都唔主動拎出黎譴責同報吿調查/拘捕進展？&rdquo;</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nRelated: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1531446/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1531446/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"1fe088140d481a904f68adf27bb3fa3c9682c0c8","tid":1531634,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b913724c185f5c13a8a6b1210ae53168c88953ac","tid":1531634,"uid":265863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾P牌仔推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568f3bd1f0fa33d13903d6db6f163faf1f63924e","tid":1531634,"uid":284264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:40:51.000Z","msg":"幫手推！"},{"pid":"3e985142e0c609f634171f7f284469d728bd451f","tid":1531634,"uid":256632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:41:04.000Z","msg":"【持續更新】香港人九月日程表<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/kEaguAX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kEaguAX</a>"},{"pid":"1d490404984def527a4d3454ee924b77a970a69d","tid":1531634,"uid":47081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:44:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0a855b1e4f6d0334236a495460056c4f268c5e79","tid":1531634,"uid":47081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:44:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6e81c39cb33b61d0bb6dc860ea1d8646122c8831","tid":1531634,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:45:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月9日美國國會復會！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style